text.tspan: Register and create a ‘you’ profile by
entering basic details and filling out our
application form. You can make a
general application or select contracts
you are interested in.
Invites you to select a Skype, telephone
or face to face interview so we can learn
about your skills and experience. If
successful you will be invited to join our
team.
Login into your Staff Zone to review your
details, view your contracts, complete
training logs and upload all information
required such as identification, tax and
payment details.
Will keep you in the loop every step of the
way, with information regarding contracts
that match your skills and location. We
believe in preparing all our teams to
maximise job satisfaction on the day and to
build a solid team environment.
